; Name ..........: GetTownHallLevel
; Description ...:
; Syntax ........: GetTownHallLevel($bFirstTime)
; Parameters ....: $bFirstTime          - a boolean value True = first time the bot has run
; Return values .: None
; Author ........: KNowJack (July 2015)
